Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.81,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight 不要回頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight 邁步出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼淚是閃閃發光的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.90,0:00:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每一步 都化為甘霖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.88,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不需要的東西就捨去 這樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.50,0:00:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在無限廣闊的心中蔓延開來喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,於受傷時刻之外　看不見的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若現在開始映入雙眸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Just Try-again
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.11,0:01:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,變得強大 抓住機會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight 無論何時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight 都要堅信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夢想絕對能實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有多遙遠 都不害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.23,0:01:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight Fight 更能感覺到明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.79,0:01:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫戰部渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.40,0:01:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了打倒支配了在遙遠天空上的星界山的多壞達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.46,0:01:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們以第七星界為目標展開了冒險旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.99,0:01:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在身處的是有趣的熱帶第六星界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.73,0:01:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,中了暗黑之劍成為魔界中人的武一郎師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.61,0:01:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在進發的途中到處追殺我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.67,0:01:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是,我們該怎樣才能救出師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.45,0:02:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天也會是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.16,0:02:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第四十二話\N悲哀的瑪達莉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.47,0:02:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底要讓我等到何時?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.98,0:02:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.03,0:02:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連把一個渡變成魔界份子也做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.78,0:02:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們的實力也只是如此嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算我多嘴了多壞達大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.66,0:02:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,行動不能順利完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.34,0:02:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全部是因為多餘的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.77,0:02:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上一次戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.97,0:02:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是你的兒子多餘的插手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡才不是在下的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要推三推四的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡、虎王、海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.80,0:02:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這三個人他們集合的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.29,0:02:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會有想像以上的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.51,0:02:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要令渡變成魔界的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.87,0:03:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,便要讓他們三人的心分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這真是好辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.11,0:03:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請交給我處理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.23,0:03:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這也許會是我給你最後的命令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我早已覺悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去吧,多支達路!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.56,0:03:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.37,0:03:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡絕對要由我來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迷失在一個不得了的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.22,0:03:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為有個傻瓜說這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說誰是傻瓜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只不過是建議而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.06,0:03:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的第六感真是不可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.53,0:03:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.89,0:03:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.93,0:03:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的…你們不要這樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.77,0:03:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什麼事便立刻吵架呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,去問問他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請問這裏是什麼地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加拉桑森林呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼,去亞索加方向的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這邊正確嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚇?什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.83,0:04:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.71,0:04:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊…又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子想想辦法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.67,0:04:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,忍法,蜘蛛絲呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.84,0:04:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為你們只顧著吵架呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,你在笑什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.24,0:04:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快救我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.92,0:04:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,差不多是時候放了他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,纏著他們的不只是我的蜘蛛絲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.52,0:04:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是真的蜘蛛絲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.58,0:04:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,連我也被纏著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也要纏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.62,0:05:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很有趣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,這次一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.74,0:05:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,(咒語)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.98,0:05:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你還這麼悠閑玩公仔嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.86,0:05:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是芭哈路大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說我在玩公仔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.09,0:05:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒這麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.33,0:05:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是普通的公仔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.91,0:05:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是普通的公仔那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.97,0:05:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在加拉桑森林裏粘上蜘蛛絲的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全部能被我控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.49,0:05:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣便能控制渡他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.49,0:06:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如你所說的一樣令他們的內心分離的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.87,0:06:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到時候就用黑龍角出擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要失敗啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.08,0:06:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於鬆脫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.64,0:06:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,趕路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.76,0:06:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.78,0:06:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊…不,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.68,0:06:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知為何突然有不好的預感…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會發生什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.29,0:06:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的,你的預感才不會中呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.33,0:06:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說什麼?混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.90,0:06:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想打嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又來了…停手呀你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是普通的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個叫虎王的家夥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.59,0:07:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣渡他們便在我的手中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.30,0:07:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然有一個不能控制,算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能控制兩個的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要他們不和便輕而易舉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.45,0:07:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.28,0:07:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?手腳自然地動…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.46,0:07:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.85,0:07:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的手自己…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟敢打我的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.72,0:07:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王,是真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.14,0:07:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和自己的意識沒關係,他在動呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭,控制不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.38,0:07:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼我們非要這樣不可?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才能感覺也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.64,0:07:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣看這個森林也有古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.75,0:07:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,虎王!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼只有他能行動自如?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果這時候古拿瑪在的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.22,0:08:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想請問一下你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你認識一個在風暴中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.63,0:08:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出海捕漁之後行蹤不明的男人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.24,0:08:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,捕漁失蹤了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.16,0:08:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他當時應該是有一個二三歲的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道,我不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打擾你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你對渡他們幹了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼只有我沒事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.80,0:09:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已無路可逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.64,0:10:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,活該呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣?想講話了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.77,0:10:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你肯講的話,我便救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.71,0:11:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你為什麼要救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.05,0:11:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為最重要的事還未問你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.68,0:11:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的臉上有什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.36,0:11:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡他們是中了死亡遙控魔術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又是魔術嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.59,0:11:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要曾粘上一次那些蜘蛛絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使全部抓掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.86,0:11:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也會留下一條用來遙控的絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此渡他們便變成那樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.01,0:11:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼我因為曾經是魔界的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以不被控制吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.89,0:12:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔界的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然是魔界的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼要跟渡在一起?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.51,0:12:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我和渡是朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子是我的新娘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.44,0:12:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至於海火子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然我不太喜歡他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.40,0:12:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是大家一起的話很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.79,0:12:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快樂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.66,0:12:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.57,0:12:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑪達莉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你有朋友的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.81,0:12:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之,一天有我在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.68,0:12:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不會讓你取渡的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.53,0:12:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你為什麼要這樣拚命?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.38,0:12:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我和渡是好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以,就算要了我的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.51,0:12:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也要保護渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼你快去救他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.53,0:12:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在他們被控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的會是自傷殘殺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.83,0:12:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我應該怎麼樣做呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我告訴你是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想渡他們被死亡遙控控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.64,0:13:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡要由我來救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種事怎麼樣也沒所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣才能救到他們?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把放那條絲的蜘蛛殺掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.18,0:13:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家夥在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.93,0:13:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有趣的事現在才開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.36,0:13:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,(咒語)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.07,0:13:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停…停手,海火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.52,0:13:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也想停呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危…危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.78,0:13:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能饒恕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.16,0:13:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,用魔神分勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夏鬼丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.71,0:13:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼破爛魔神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.22,0:13:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍星丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.12,0:14:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.46,0:14:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,囉嗦,我要和他打!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.12,0:14:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.08,0:14:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死亡遙控的蜘蛛便是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.83,0:15:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做得好…再打吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.58,0:15:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大件事了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.46,0:15:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家夥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.16,0:16:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼我會在夏鬼丸上的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.80,0:16:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦,我怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.14,0:16:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,你清醒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.60,0:16:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.24,0:16:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死亡遙控那家夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.21,0:16:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只差一步竟然先失手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.21,0:16:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雪京芭、節芭利上了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.10,0:16:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.89,0:16:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.39,0:16:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要大意,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.03,0:16:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍星丸,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.19,0:16:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.90,0:16:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心點啊,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.19,0:16:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們能看穿黑龍角的魔幻術嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個也不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪個才是真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.32,0:16:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.23,0:17:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話便用這個吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.95,0:17:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那個了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.85,0:17:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個是正體了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.59,0:17:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.93,0:17:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.48,0:17:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.33,0:17:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要小看我們啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.60,0:17:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.39,0:18:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.70,0:18:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們沒有我的話便什麼也做不成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你竟敢說呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,猛虎變形!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.07,0:18:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一口氣分勝負吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.52,0:18:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這混蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.79,0:18:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,變形,飛龍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.62,0:19:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飛龍光擊拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.52,0:19:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雪京芭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.91,0:19:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,節芭利,雪京芭被擊落了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.11,0:19:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,撤退了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.81,0:19:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為虎王收拾了那只蜘蛛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.73,0:19:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以,我們才能自由嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.54,0:19:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總算是謝謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但追根究底也是虎王你找我吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.01,0:19:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊,我什麼時候!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.04,0:19:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.43,0:19:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餵,你們停一停呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.77,0:20:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑪達莉斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.84,0:20:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這家夥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.27,0:20:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑪達莉斯,住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.84,0:20:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你讓開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.78,0:20:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是不殺渡不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.03,0:20:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會讓你殺我好朋友的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.68,0:20:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快讓開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.47,0:20:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然連你也殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.56,0:20:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我跟渡是好朋友呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.53,0:20:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以,就算要了我的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.02,0:20:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也要保護渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.88,0:20:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑪達莉斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死吧,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑪達莉斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑪達莉斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,背叛者嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.88,0:21:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑪達莉斯,振作一點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.61,0:21:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.92,0:21:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的…很想要朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是…我的朋友呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.99,0:21:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.20,0:21:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝…你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.48,0:21:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑪達莉斯…
